metadata.name: EccentricConcentric  #71
metadata.description:
pixelwank & Qotonana are proud to present 'EccentricConcentric' 

Exploring moire and concentric shapes, the results of EccentricConcentric are greater than the sum of its parts. 

Thanks to our collectors, supporters and the FxHash community. 

Press 's' to save canvas 
Press '2' for 1500x2000 png
Press '3' for 2250x3000 png
Press '4' for 3000x4000 png 
Press '8' for 6000x8000 png (very slow)

Made with p5.js 
© Pixelwank & Qotonana 2022 

R.I.F.F.
Remember It's For Fun <3
